snippet.title: Nekodancer - Trailer [EN]
snippet.description:
Now available on http://www.nekodancer.com !

Nekodancer is a massively multiplayer dance game, where you compete with your friends to be the best dancer on the catfloor! Enter ANY Youtube video in your playlist, and dance along the arrows!

But be careful, some power-ups will try to bring you down the podium!

Be the best to earn a lot of sushis and customize your cat!

A game by Atelier 801 - www.atelier801.com
